#funfact sunday #easter style! 💐

🐇 in #estonia, easter goes by different names – ületõusmispüha (resurrection day), lihavõtted (meat-taking day), munadepüha (egg holiday), kiigepühad (swing holiday). and we use onion skins and beets to dye eggs. 👇🏼
raw text:
